description: Demolition of the existing dwellinghouses to provide for the comprehensive residential redevelopment of the Brookhill Estate. The proposal includes the construction of residential dwellings (Use Class C3), improvements to public realm including hard and soft landscaping, highways works, car parking, cycle parking, refuse and recycling storage, plant, external amenity space and playspace.
